token_info.name: Uhhhh... Hornk?
token_info.description: My first attempt at bringing a creature to the 3rd dimension. I'm so sorry little guy, blink twice if you want me to burn you... No? Cool, so what should I call you... Hornk? Shake your head if you hate it... Awesome! I love you too pal, come in for a hug! | Seriously this is the price for learning | @HeitzStudio
